mature enough to have
a cup of coffee together.

27:18.304 --> 27:19.885
So, I’ve missed you.
I’ve missed you.

27:19.972 --> 27:23.464
Um, you know,
’cause you were such
a big part of my life.

27:23.559 --> 27:25.550
Me too.

27:28.856 --> 27:31.233
The other night, I woke up
in the middle of the night.

27:31.317 --> 27:32.523
3:20?

27:32.610 --> 27:35.067
Of course. When else?

27:36.489 --> 27:38.980
And I... reached
out to touch you.

27:39.075 --> 27:41.111
But I wasn’t there.

27:42.829 --> 27:44.911
