A pathologist, on and off.

27:49.544 --> 27:51.455
He also does stand—up
on the weekends.

27:51.546 --> 27:54.583
That’s nice. Sounds nice.

27:54.674 --> 27:58.337
l, um, I’ve been—
I’ve been sort of seeing
someone too.

27:58.427 --> 28:01.590
Uh, from the Bureau.
lt’s, uh, nothing serious.

28:03.015 --> 28:05.722
I’m glad for you.
