28:05.810 --> 28:08.096
[ Chuckles ]

28:11.107 --> 28:13.439
I want to say something.

28:17.029 --> 28:18.940
Since we split,
I’ve been thinking.

28:22.618 --> 28:26.736
And... I wanted
to see you again
because I wanted to see—

28:26.831 --> 28:28.367
See if it was a mistake?

28:28.457 --> 28:30.163
Yes.

28:31.919 --> 28:33.580
Me too.

28:33.671 --> 28:35.582
I mean, we had so much.

28:39.385 --> 28:42.923
But it was a mistake.
We don’t belong together.

28:44.724 --> 28:45.964
I know.

28:50.396 --> 28:52.512
Now we don’t have
to question that anymore.

28:53.941 --> 28:55.806
