he wanted to rush things along,

29:58.130 --> 30:00.507
move on to the next client.

30:00.591 --> 30:04.800
I hope they weren’t a couple,
because Rachel deserved
a lot more than Akshay.

30:04.887 --> 30:06.752
[Sighs]

