used the fat beetles to
run through the GO mass spec.

30:30.913 --> 30:34.155
Exactly, and in the beetles
that were on Monica Craig,

30:34.250 --> 30:36.411
I discovered the presence
of methylone.

30:36.502 --> 30:38.663
Bath salts.
That’s a recreational drug.

30:38.754 --> 30:42.667
Particularly nasty.
Last year, the DEA. issued
an emergency ban on it.

30:42.758 --> 30:46.592
I can’t imagine a cancer patient
in her condition
using recreational drugs.

30:46.679 --> 30:48.670
Are you thinking
she was poisoned?

30:48.764 --> 30:51.927
If she overdosed on methylone,
that would explain
why Mrs. Craig died...

30:52.018 --> 30:54.430
before her cancer reached
its most advanced stage.

30:54.520 --> 30:56.636
Methylone doesn’t
just present in tissue.

30:56.731 --> 30:58.892
It would also be
evident in bone marrow.

30:58.983 --> 31:01.520
If I take samples,
and | find
excessive levels, then—

31:01.610 --> 31:03.225
Then we’re dealing
with two murders.

31:09.326 --> 31:12.944
