you can’t just leave it
to me how to bury you.

31:15.458 --> 31:16.698
I told you I trust you.

31:16.792 --> 31:20.535
But your funeral
is your last message
to your loved ones.

31:20.629 --> 31:22.415
Especially Christine,
if she’s a child.

31:22.506 --> 31:24.337
